Solving ODEs in R language, as example for test this class:
```R func <- function(t, x, parms) { with(as.list(c(parms, x)), {
dP <- a * P - b * C * P dC <- b * P * C - c * C
list(c(dP, dC)) }) }
y0 <- c(P = 2, C = 1) parms <- c(a = 0.1, b = 0.1, c = 0.1) out <- ode(y = y0, times = 0:100, func, parms = parms)
head(out) plot(out) ```
